      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ASTON RENNES (3) missed the frame latest when fifth at Warragul (26.45) but scored three back at Healesville (17.05). Scored previously at this trip. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Better than last start and worth following up. ELEVATE (2) crossed over from out wide last start before finishing second (25.90) at this track in a Grade 5 over 450m. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Well-placed to take this out. INSTANT ACTION (4) was well fancied in betting last start but could only manage 3.5 lengths away in third (24.47). Overdue and expected to feature again. KING PLUM (1) is new to this circuit but not to be underestimated.",
